<h2 id="benefits-of-mdx">Benefits of MDX</h2>
<p>The benefit of MDX is simply that you can use components inside your Markdown.
Hey look a button: <button class="btn btn-primary"> Click Me!</button></p>
<h2 id="code">Code</h2>
<p>Create a Remix.run project using <code>npx create-remix@latest</code> and choose TypeScript and to host it on Vercel.</p>
<h3 id="modify-tsconfigjson">Modify <code>tsconfig.json</code></h3>
<ul>
<li>Set <code>&quot;target&quot;</code> to <code>&quot;ES2020&quot;</code></li>
<li>Add the line<code>&quot;module&quot;: &quot;ES2020&quot;,</code></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="install-packages">Install packages</h3>
<p><code>npm install --save-exact mdx-bundler front-matter rehype-highlight remark-gfm rehype-autolink-headings rehype-toc rehype-slug esbuild@0.12.09</code></p>
<p>Create a folder in your project <code>app/utils</code> and add these files:</p>
