<h2 id="create-your-first-post">Create your first post</h2>
<p>Create a folder in your project called <code>blog-posts</code> and add a file <code>blog-posts/first-post.mdx</code>:</p>
<div class="relative"><pre><code class="hljs language-mdx">---
title: &quot;First post&quot;
description: &quot;the first post.&quot;
date: 2022-02-03
---

I&#x27;m trying something out with Remix.

## code

```js
import { Outlet } from &quot;remix&quot;;

export default function Blog() {
  return (
    &lt;div className=&quot;flex justify-center&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div className=&quot;prose lg:prose-xl py-10&quot;&gt;
        &lt;Outlet /&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  );
}
```
</code></pre></div>
<h2 id="features">Features</h2>
<h3 id="tailwind-css">Tailwind CSS</h3>
<p>See <a href="https://github.com/remix-run/remix/tree/main/examples/tailwindcss">https://github.com/remix-run/remix/tree/main/examples/tailwindcss</a> for how to configure Tailwind CSS.</p>
<h3 id="code-syntax-highlighting">Code Syntax Highlighting</h3>
<h3 id="hosting-on-vercel-flyio">Hosting on <strike>Vercel</strike> Fly.io</h3>
<p>I ran into some problems with esbuild EACCESS errors on Vercel and I&#x27;m now hosting this on Fly.io</p>
<h2 id="source-code--template">Source code / template</h2>
